lead_paragraph: Bangladesh were all out for 296 in their second innings to set England a target of 273 to win the second and final test at the Shere Bangla National Stadium on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Bangladesh Set England 273 to Win Second Test
headline.main: Bangladesh Set England 273 to Win Second Test
